parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Looks like this clock is powered by batteries. Maybe I could use them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Feel free to look around. I have a leak to deal with upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaOp.Don’t worry, Father. We won’t disturb your belongings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaEx.Keep an eye on the nun. I can handle this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.I didn’t mean anything by what I said.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaDe.Am I the only one being hurt by this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaEx.Oh, God. It’s so silly… You are like my time machine…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx.I was just… Looking for the restroom.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx>.Oh! How rude of me. Let me unlock my bathroom… ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx>.I keep it locked so the parishioners don't wander into my medicine cabinet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.Is everything okay, 1Hero? Our trip to the demon world certainly must have you frazzled.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Careful, 1Hero. Those monsters will try to manipulate you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.I feel I’m close to figuring something out, but not sure…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Well… I better get back to it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.What the hell is 1Hero doing in there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaEx^.Oh, yes. I told you it was nice.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOpNo1.Good golly! Smells like sex in there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.Hope I didn’t cut you rabbits short.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlEx.How about next time use Judy’s bedroom? Quite a bit more comfortable, I would think.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlDe.You think the nun would mind some stains on the sheets?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlEx.Like I tell 1Hero… It’s not fun unless you get caught from time to time.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoDe^.I wish I had your outlook on life, Carol.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlEx.You’ll get there. Just need to get 1Hero to fuck that stick out of your ass.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Uhh… I don’t think that’s how the saying goes.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFlEx^.Hey. Someone’s got to look out for us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaHaOpNo3.Haha. A lot of good it did.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.Well… What’s left to tease me about? I’ve done it all with you ladies… and your daughters.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaFlEx.Don’t worry. I’m sure we can find lots of stuff to talk about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.You’re saying a police officer found Sister Judy and Kimberly near the rift?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I sent him there… Bobby Rinaldi… He’s keeping them at the mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe^.What about the demons? Did he see them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.They are not with the girls. The girls are alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.We have to get over there and save them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Hold on, Father… It might be a trap.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe^.You think Lilith is trying to lure the priest into a trap?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I sense a trap… Lillian knows that Father Solomon would go after them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Arianna and I will go get them and bring them back here… The crosses will protect them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Bobby said the portal closed. But we should hurry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe^.What about the cops? Will they let you in?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Bobby will let us in. He trusts me now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp.I just hope Sister Judy is okay… Lilith did a number on her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.I can bless them… I can undo the brainwashing Lilith has put upon them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "NeFlEx.Come on… new Madalyn. I’ll show you the way.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m going to talk to Bobby… He’ll let us search the mansion… He has to.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe^.I don’t trust cops, but we need to be able to search that mansion.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.Get a few hours of rest, Henry… I’ll try and do the same.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrFrEx^.Diana and I can find those amulets… We’re built for this.");
